'''兒茶酚-''O''-甲基轉移酶''' ('''COMT'''; {{EC number|2.1.1.6}})是分解[[兒茶酚胺|兒茶酚胺]](如[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]、[[腎上腺素|腎上腺素]]和[[去甲腎上腺素|去甲腎上腺素]])的幾種酶之一。在人體，'''兒茶酚-''O''-甲基轉移酶'''由'''COMT'''[[基因|基因]]編碼<ref name="pmid1572656">{{cite journal | vauthors = Grossman MH, Emanuel BS, Budarf ML | title = Chromosomal mapping of the human catechol-O-methyltransferase gene to 22q11.1-q11.2 | journal = Genomics | volume = 12 | issue = 4 | pages = 822–5 | date = April 1992 | pmid = 1572656 | doi = 10.1016/0888-7543(92)90316-K | url =  | issn =  }}</ref>。鑒於在一些疾病中兒茶酚胺的調節受損，數種藥物以'''COMT'''為標靶，調整其活性來控制兒茶酚胺的濃度<ref name="pmid11873938">{{cite journal | vauthors = Tai CH, Wu RM | title = Catechol-O-methyltransferase and Parkinson's disease | journal = Acta Med. Okayama | volume = 56 | issue = 1 | pages = 1–6 | date = February 2002 | pmid = 11873938 | doi =  | url =  | issn =  }}</ref>。

COMT在1957年由[[生物化學家|生物化學家]] [[朱利叶斯·阿克塞尔罗德|朱利叶斯·阿克塞尔罗德]]發現<ref name="pmid13467217">{{cite journal | vauthors = Axelrod J | title = O-Methylation of Epinephrine and Other Catechols in vitro and in vivo | journal = Science | volume = 126 | issue = 3270 | pages = 400–1 | date = August 1957 | pmid = 13467217 | doi = 10.1126/science.126.3270.400 | url =  | issn =  }}</ref>。

== 功能 ==

兒茶酚-''O''-甲基轉移酶參與了[[儿茶酚胺|儿茶酚胺]][[神经递质|神经递质]]([[多巴胺|多巴胺]]、[[肾上腺素|肾上腺素]]以及[[去甲肾上腺素|去甲肾上腺素]])的去活性化，它在兒茶酚胺上加入由 [[S-腺苷甲硫氨酸|S-腺苷甲硫氨酸]] (SAM)給予的[[甲基|甲基]]。具有[[鄰苯二酚|鄰苯二酚]]結構的物質都是COMT的[[基質|基質]]，如兒茶酚雌激素以及含有鄰苯二酚的黃酮類化合物。
[[L-多巴|L-多巴]]，兒茶酚胺的[[前驅物|前驅物]]，是COMT重要的基質。COMT抑制劑如[[恩他卡朋|恩他卡朋]]，使L-多巴不被COMT分解為[[3-O-甲基多巴|3-O-甲基多巴]](3-OMD)，剩下[[芳香族L-氨基酸脫羧酶|芳香族L-氨基酸脫羧酶]](DACC)途徑，同時增加其半衰期<ref name="PD">{{Cite journal
 | author = [[H._M._Ruottinen|H. M. Ruottinen]] & [[U._K._Rinne|U. K. Rinne]]
 | title = COMT inhibition in the treatment of Parkinson's disease
 | journal = [[Journal_of_neurology|Journal of neurology]]
 | volume = 245
 | issue = 11 Suppl 3
 | pages = P25–P34
 | date = 1998 November
 | pmid = 9808337
}}</ref><ref name="pmidhttp://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9591519">{{cite journal| author=Goetz CG| title=Influence of COMT inhibition on levodopa pharmacology and therapy. | journal=Neurology | year= 1998 | volume= 50 | issue= 5 Suppl 5 | pages= S26-30 | pmid=9591519 | doi= | pmc= | url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=9591519  }} </ref>。延長L-多巴藥物時效。

由COMT催化的反應包含:
* [[多巴胺|多巴胺]] → {{tsl|en|3-Methoxytyramine||3-Methoxytyramine}}
* {{tsl|en|DOPAC||DOPAC}} → HVA ({{tsl|en|homovanillic acid|高香草酸}})
* [[去甲肾上腺素|去甲肾上腺素]] → [[去甲變腎上腺素|去甲變腎上腺素]]
* [[肾上腺素|肾上腺素]] → [[變腎上腺素|變腎上腺素]]
* {{tsl|en|Dihydroxyphenylethylene glycol||Dihydroxyphenylethylene glycol}} (DOPEG) → {{tsl|en|Methoxyhydroxyphenylglycol||Methoxyhydroxyphenylglycol}} (MOPEG)
* {{tsl|en|3,4-Dihydroxymandelic acid||3,4-Dihydroxymandelic acid}} (DOMA) → {{tsl|en|Vanillylmandelic acid||Vanillylmandelic acid}} (VMA)
在腦部，依賴COMT的多巴胺降解於低[[多巴胺轉運體|多巴胺轉運體]](DAT)表現的區域特別重要，如[[前額葉皮質|前額葉皮質]]<ref name="pmid12535946">{{cite journal | vauthors = Matsumoto M, Weickert CS, Akil M, Lipska BK, Hyde TM, Herman MM, Kleinman JE, Weinberger DR | title = Catechol O-methyltransferase mRNA expression in human and rat brain: evidence for a role in cortical neuronal function | journal = Neuroscience | volume = 116 | issue = 1 | pages = 127–37 | year = 2003 | pmid = 12535946 | doi = 10.1016/S0306-4522(02)00556-0 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Karoum F, Chrapusta SJ, Egan MF | title = 3-Methoxytyramine is the Major Metabolite of Released Dopamine in the Rat Frontal Cortex: Reassessment of the Effects of Antipsychotics on the Dynamics of Dopamine Release and Metabolism in the Frontal Cortex, Nucleus Accumbens, and Striatum by a Simple T | journal = Journal of Neurochemistry | volume = 63 | issue = 3 | pages = 972–9 | year = 2002 | pmid = 7914228 | doi = 10.1046/j.1471-4159.1994.63030972.x }}</ref>。

== 命名 ==

''COMT''是編碼這個酶的基因的名字。名字中的'''''O'''''意指[[氧|氧]]，不是''{{tsl|en|arene substitution patterns||ortho}}''。

== COMT抑制劑 ==

[[COMT抑制劑|COMT抑制劑]]包括{{tsl|en|tolcapone|托卡朋}}以及[[恩他卡朋|恩他卡朋]]，常被用於治療[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]<ref name="pmid17894650">{{cite journal | vauthors = Bonifácio MJ, Palma PN, Almeida L, Soares-da-Silva P | title = Catechol-O-methyltransferase and its inhibitors in Parkinson's disease | journal = CNS Drug Rev | volume = 13 | issue = 3 | pages = 352–79 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17894650 | doi = 10.1111/j.1527-3458.2007.00020.x | url =  | issn =  }}</ref>。

